                     <join result="defendantPunishment" targOrder="Y" targets="t18080713-15-defend196 t18080713-15-punish94"></join>
               Imprisoned One Year in Newgate
            </rs> and <rs id="t18080713-15-punish95" type="punishmentDescription">
                     <interp inst="t18080713-15-punish95" type="punishmentCategory" value="miscPunish"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18080713-15-punish95" type="punishmentSubcategory" value="fine"></interp>
                     <join result="defendantPunishment" targOrder="Y" targets="t18080713-15-defend196 t18080713-15-punish95"></join>
               fined One Shilling
            </rs>.</p>
               <p>London jury, before Mr. Common Serjeant.</p>
